text: Gif ðonne huelc mon ðæt uord cwæðe ðæt ne me siae min wic ðon <alefedran> ðon oþrum higum to brucenne ne minum aerfeweardum.
Ðonne wite he ðæt hit naes nefre cristes cirican land ne nenges monnes boclond aer min.
And ðonne se monne ieondðence & asmeaie be oðerra monna boclondum ie in friþstolum ie butan.
Huader hio megen hiora agen sellan oððe on hiora lif gan sue him leof siae oððe for huðu min scyle beon <un> ðon oðrum monnum hiora.
